headline: Texas Pacific Land: 17% Of My Portfolio, And I'm Not Done Buying
summary: In 2017-2024, Texas Pacific Land returned 37% per year, beating the impressive 18% annual return of the Nasdaq Composite. See why I'm bullish on TPL stock.
